      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Draft a warm, personalized re-engagement email for this at-risk client:\n\nClient: {{ $('Log Incomplete Records').item.json['Client Name'] }}\nLast Invoice: {{ $('Log Incomplete Records').item.json['Last Invoice Date'] }}\nLast Email Reply: {{ $('Log Incomplete Records').item.json['Last Email Reply Date'] }}\nLast Meeting:{{ $('Log Incomplete Records').item.json['Last Meeting Date'] }}\nHealth Score: {{ $('Combine Client Score').item.json.healthScore }}\nReason: {{ $('Combine Client Score').item.json.reason }}\n\nWrite a short, warm email from the account manager that:\n- Does NOT sound automated\n- References how long it has been since last contact\n- Offers something specific (check-in call, resource, or update)\n- Keeps it under 150 words\n- Uses a friendly, professional tone",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are an experienced account manager writing personalized client outreach. Your emails are warm, genuine, and action-oriented. Never use generic templates or corporate jargon."
        }
      },
